{
  "stem": "8842.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could all go home because they're going to open up a ghetto, and we're going to be all put into a ghetto, so they don't need us there anymore.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we just walked home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But before we left this place, we had a terrible-- we smelled something horrible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a fire that is burning flesh.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could smell-- in those days, being as stupid as I was, I said, Mommy, is there somebody burning a chicken?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in those days, you used to hold the chicken over a fire to take all her feathers out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You wouldn't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're too young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But a chicken was not being bought in those days like you buy it now, all clean.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You used to flick it and used to do all the cleaning, and then come home and burn over a little fire to burn off all the-- that's the kind of smell it was, and even worse.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was so, so bad, and we didn't understand what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We found out later a disastrous thing what happened, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll come to that point.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't know much about our father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nothing at all, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we tried to put ourselves together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Our house was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nobody broke in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a couple of days later, we had somebody that came in to tell us that they saw my father in the street among prisoners on the street, going in the middle of the city.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where did you see it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they told us which prison this man will be-- how my father was there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother immediately ran there, and she-- sure enough, she found out that my father is there, and he's very sick.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
